	case - modify case of all letters in a file

This filepp module provides to modules: toupper and tolower.

The toupper module converts all letters to upper case.

The tolower module converts all letters to lower case.

There is a simple test file included with this module.  To test the
for module use the following commands (the file "test" is in this
directory):

filepp -m toupper.pm test.in
filepp -m tolower.pm test.in

For full documentation on how to use filepp and the case module read
the filepp man page. 

